{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"96a4a85bb1","title":"陈伯达等审查交响乐《海港》时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a1345f356d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":9,"articleId":"96a4a85bb1","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"文学艺术","id":"5387dec24b","type":"主题"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"叶群","id":"62ff3f0cef","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"737e233e6b","type":"title","text":"陈伯达等审查交响乐《海港》时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"96a4a85bb1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2930a744dc","type":"paragraph","text":"〖十月九日晚，伯达、戚本禹、叶群等同志在首都剧场看了中央乐团新创作的第二个交响乐《海港》，看后，伯达同志作了简短指示。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"96a4a85bb1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7b5d1fa42","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志指示：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"96a4a85bb1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05cd0ccbdf","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志最近工作很忙，今天晚上叫我们先来听一听，这个戏，演唱还是很好的，江青同志想听一下，希望能够录下音，交给江青同志。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"96a4a85bb1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d81d6711e4","type":"paragraph","text":"整个戏的场面还是可以的，有的地方机器声太吵，应再静一些。为了慎重起见，还是希望江青同志看过后，再当众演出。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"96a4a85bb1","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}